        <item>
            <title>Version 1.4.2-1</title>
            <link>https://github.com/Bengerthelorf/macIconChanger</link>
            <sparkle:version>2026031100</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.4.2-1</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <pubDate>Wed, 11 Mar 2026 08:17:36 +0000</pubDate>
            <enclosure url="https://github.com/Bengerthelorf/macIconChanger/releases/download/v1.4.2-1/IconChanger.dmg"
            sparkle:edSignature="y3vsIT3Pbcj+FrGlYI+BoYV0RDN+690dQwyk430Tt5cih97uFdZyQTPGz0AHTDMI6Fv9vGj7dGE6ojgCpvAoAQ==" length="5230892"
            type="application/octet-stream"/>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[
                <h2>Version 1.4.2-1 — Hotfix</h2>
                <p>Fixes raw JSON error messages being displayed to users.</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Fixed:</strong> 404 responses now show "No Icons Found" instead of a raw JSON error</li>
                    <li><strong>Fixed:</strong> API errors display clean messages instead of dumping JSON response bodies</li>
                    <li><strong>Fixed:</strong> Connection test shows clear messages for 429, 401/403, and 5xx errors</li>
                </ul>
                <h2>Version 1.4.2</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>New:</strong> Icon Favorites — right-click any icon to save it to favorites</li>
                    <li><strong>New:</strong> Icon History — view past icon changes for each app</li>
                    <li><strong>New:</strong> Folder Icon Customization — add folders and change their icons</li>
                    <li><strong>New:</strong> API Rate Limiting — monthly usage tracking with configurable limits</li>
                    <li><strong>New:</strong> Configurable retry count and request timeout in Settings</li>
                    <li><strong>New:</strong> Distinct error messages for different API failure modes</li>
                    <li><strong>Fixed:</strong> Dock Preview hidden for Folders filter, filters apply correctly</li>
                    <li><strong>Fixed:</strong> Dock Preview icons refresh consistently with sidebar</li>
                    <li><strong>Fixed:</strong> Infinite spinner for folders in Local icons section</li>
                    <li><strong>Docs:</strong> 30 language translations on the documentation site</li>
                </ul>
                ]]>
            </description>
        </item>
